{
  "title": "Citrusy Zesty Egyptian Shaggy Papillote",
  "description": "A post-workout, low-carb Egyptian dish featuring doubanjiang, wrapped in a shaggy papillote. Perfect for a quick, citrusy meal after a long run.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
  "diet": [
    "low-carb",
